<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>OMORI on Secret Garden in Urlicht</title><link>https://mahoutsukaiUrlicht.github.io/tags/omori/</link><description>Recent content in OMORI on Secret Garden in Urlicht</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 09 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://mahoutsukaiUrlicht.github.io/tags/omori/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>魅影</title><link>https://mahoutsukaiUrlicht.github.io/fragments/%E9%AD%85%E5%BD%B1/</link><pubDate>Mon, 09 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mahoutsukaiUrlicht.github.io/fragments/%E9%AD%85%E5%BD%B1/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;混沌将我缠绕。&lt;br&gt;
我被围困在一片寂静中。恶魔的谄媚再次出现，盘踞在内心的不安声音再次响起。&lt;br&gt;
我冰冷的双手扼住了自己的颈项，遏制着自己的睡意，拼命地对抗着来自深渊的引力。可是眼前一阵又一阵五彩斑斓的光束盘旋着。我的身体围绕着无形的中心旋转，无法挣脱地向深渊滑去。恐惧使我双眼紧闭。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>